name: Miami Vending Machines
overview: Miami Vending Machines, Snacks & More was founded in 2006 by Eric Neidorf. The business is family owned and operated. We understand the value of service and have built our business on this strong commitment. We offer a full line of vending machines, snacks, paper and plastic goods and vending services to businesses, schools, and facilities in Dade, Broward & Palm Beach, Florida. We are a full service vending & snack company that strives to provide hands-on customer service. For more information please visit our website http://www.miamivendingmachines.com
